0","tid":1814440,"uid":81879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:36:54.000Z","msg":"而家係勇武要退場屌緊和理非喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:40:02.000Z","msg":"有人扮咋<br />\n係真既點會驚死人唔知佢有做野咁開哂POST講呀<br />\n想攞威定攞安慰?<br />\n<br />\n但係樓主就覺得會有真勇武用篇文黎催淚<br />\n洗撚希罕你地D眼淚咩<br />\n<br />\n又要做又要屌既由始至終都係得國難五金架咋<br />\n仲邊有人咁小學雞"},{"pid":"bf56e1057844a84fbdcab57389f12c9c6eaa2108","tid":1814440,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}